			</p>
		</div>
	</header>
	<div style="clear: both;"></div>
	<nav>
		<div id="nav_bar">
			<ul>
				<li>
					<a href="#"><img src="../assets/images/glowna.png" width="20px" height="20px" style="vertical-align:middle" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;home</a>
